## App Design

"I develop innovative mobile and desktop applications with a strong emphasis on functionality, security, and performance.
From AI-powered assistants to finance and productivity tools, I build applications that solve real-world problems while ensuring a smooth user experience."

Projects:

Voice Assistant (NLP, Task Automation, Smart Home Control)
Basic Weather App (Tkinter, PyQt, API-based Weather Updates)
Chat Application (Networking, Socket Programming, Data Security)
BMI Calculator (GUI-based Application)
Password Generator (Security, Randomization)
Student Grade Tracker (Java, Data Processing)
Online Quiz Platform (Java, Interactive Quiz System)
Simple Banking Application (Java, Fundamental Banking Operations)
Travel Itinerary Planner (Destination-based Planning, Maps, Budget Calculation)
